Package queue.wrapper

Class QueueWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • queue.wrapper.QueueWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Queue
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    QueueWrapperLimit, QueueWrapperLock, QueueWrapperSem, QueueWrapperSync
    public abstract class QueueWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Queue
    Abstract base class for any Queue Wrapper. Serves as base in the decorator paradigm.

    For methods "implemented", it's up to the implementation of QueueObject how it's done, while insert(int) and retrieve() are methods that HAVE TO be implemented in the Wrapper, based on its policy.

    Author:
    Cristiano Salerno
